    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic just made Claude agents DREAM.",
      "checksum": "sha256:77f810ec84e4eeed056f67a78ab918c51fde9feb7d4f8625f57bda2018500e3d",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Live from Code with Claude. Four primitives, one launch, one gotcha.",
      "checksum": "sha256:727c10ca802cc8300fbba835bbe303b34ac6f280f35b30cc5e306171f5aa1014",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 6
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "But the headline isn't dreaming. Three of these shipped today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d6b4047585d30dee0416102620563d78947d64f8269320aa67e38f23acf53092",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 17
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "One is gated behind a form. Can you guess which?",
      "checksum": "sha256:c389e2150aad89dff0020e58719e575ec1a3a95ee420907107b6f416195b0668",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Because here's the line-up. Dreaming. Outcomes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f27eae265a94a010b5ee4dbf0c7a051b77513c275c14b8bb556b2203ab3d92dd",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 37
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Multiagent orchestration. Webhooks. Three are public beta and live on the Claude Platform right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c23172a80f88c059bfe731c6e4405f75826952bb7f28f743d35ab48e2bbb7cc",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 6.0836281179138325,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "One, the named flagship, is research preview only.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9fcf2ce1ef0644b6d1835fea0d3aa568da1348aebf0c6885f56afd4827a245c2",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "That's the twist. First, dreaming. The gated one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ea9db502340903e4bf430bcc54096c230bddb16c8c748bb56b83d02952dfdc8",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Your agent reviews its past sessions, extracts patterns, and curates memories, so the next agent starts smarter than the last.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8d46b622ff39966bed6febeca84d3e0d0eee646bcb36f3db5e8bee7fe93bf3dd",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 7.151746031746032,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Sleep-time learning, basically. And yes, most of you can't touch it yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93cea82cb99c85b5f5dc7cbb21ac253de03a26ecf5a01d7845c3d4a12eddcc12",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 94
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Request access at the form. Then there's outcomes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:339bad622ce565ca65e9bf5eee140867e3d37537ea3c8f53e7669e48ade0a088",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Public beta, live today. You write a rubric.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1e3cfc2ba73f9a75aa2f5a0d6848bf3fa82aa5bf043e0e4fefac7ed37168116b",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 114
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "A separate grader checks the output in its own context window.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b9ce66b552a5b267436be89707fb2930769ee103e522bdc982a84c8c7fe24738",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The agent iterates until it clears the bar.",
      "checksum": "sha256:61f7419e092dc96a81bc61f79ee774825e5bd04e0da3af8d5e1d7879de3a4e38",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Plus ten points on task success versus standard prompting.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e1050f4b529cd0b2c0f31362ccd7e9fae0249d05786f3af77eb263ceef629c39",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 141
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Stop eyeballing drafts. And while one agent grades, another delegates.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7dd604a161e51ec2fe9d5d85e53150fa0a9928405c0bbc8d4f27c7866e6e5737",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 150
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Multiagent orchestration lets a lead agent farm work to specialists running in parallel, on a shared filesystem, with their own tools.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c8ef062b52c17f05e483f19a33e68fa7bea24fcad4deece68dd07a7f08bef31e",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 8.034104308390022,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Harvey hit roughly six times completion rate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f829fd70a4d8d5542bdd50354fe74f8afad8cbeb97c179302afa884453a86e2b",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 181
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "That's not a demo number. That's a legal-AI production deployment.",
      "checksum": "sha256:950297c33c6c20f912ab2c4bcb792534156c19381df089ffccc972362a73b7c4",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 188
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Plus webhooks, to know the moment work is actually done.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a3541a55670f35310f4f2d5599d63b91526086f166bffe7022d3b766c02244e9",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 198
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Stop polling. Subscribe to a webhook. If you've ever wired a polling loop you already hate, this is the receipt.",
      "checksum": "sha256:daed1fe20d83c430e1ff4bfaf24e0809a5a2d5ca24a1ab59fb4be07525bb7281",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 6.408707482993197,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 208
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The community already called it out: webhooks are what finally close the loop for real production workflows.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6dd6c8638253a9cda79ba6961c0f769269a9139d6392a19139b2eebbffb603ab",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 6.130068027210885,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Here's why this lands. The beta header ships in the SDK, and the verification question, which agent earned the result, is finally on the table.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74715fe39e0db1c09a530a08ce6521b9407c206ca6bc0fb88dc66332bf4490df",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 9.102222222222222,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 245
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "So is Anthropic about to lock in the production-agent moat, or did dreaming get gated for a reason?",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c35ec6581dbeb92162ecdbfa5b7c82eaf5d87b1521f591ea5fdf312eadf3470",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Let me know in the comments. And subscribe for more AI news.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1782d9ad69f1c9d62be069e5693599bbf96c3359b39892f2db4c71142810cedf",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 288
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "So, available today on the Claude Platform.",
      "checksum": "sha256:97652df40e71fdea8d42808c9cce0aea024e8f28ceac3bafcf35e57cfc939952",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "The plumbing shipped. Dreaming, the named one, is the one you have to ask for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ba17041d7e19dc2538977062702554b7e5fc55f46db58f330e68b4cb7c1af44",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 307
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed8ab98bd7df91d3b58e78eff21993418ad4b085b0557e8f6564adfb92975283",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 322
    }
  ]
}